Commissioner, ladies and gentlemen, over and above this negotiation, the issue at stake is the will of the European Union to provide small and medium-sized enterprises with the favourable environment that they need and to use access to public procurement as an extraordinary lever for growth and employment; 
          also
         at stake is the need to provide legal certainty, within the European Union, between the international legal system, European law and national laws.
